author: Brett Hollander, WBAL
title: Jamison Hensley On Dennis Pitta's Future With Brett Hollander
text:
If player does not show correctly, click here to listen . 
Dennis Pitta is practicing, but does that mean he will actually play in the NFL or for the Ravens again? Jamison Hensley from ESPN.com talks with Brett about what he is up against. 
Pitta practiced for the first time since September of 2014. He has only played in 7 games since the Ravens won the Super Bowl at the end of the 2012 season.
